The paper also discusses domain adaptation, which is a technique used to improve the performance of ML models on specific domains, suggesting that it could belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses distributed computing, which could suggest that it belongs to the cs.DS (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) sub-category.
